com.zendesk.sdk.logger

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zendesk.sdk.logger.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends Object
    Simple wrapper around the android log

    This logger won't log if this is a debug build as specified by isLoggable(). The default behaviour is that it won't log until setLoggable(boolean) is called with true as the argument.
